text: Danuta Nowak-Stachow (born 22 August 1934) is a Polish gymnast. She competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics, winning a bronze medal at the 1956 Games. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gdynia Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Poland Category:Medalists at the 1956 Summer Olympics
